List out names of tables available from OxCOVID19 Database

Source: R/utilities.R
list_tables.Rd

List out names of tables available from OxCOVID19 Database

list_tables(con = connect_oxcovid19())

Arguments

con

A PqConnection class object specifying the PostgreSQL connection to OxCOVID19 Database. This is produced by connect_oxcovid19 function

Value

A vector of table names available from OxCOVID19 Database

Author

Ernest Guevarra

Examples

list_tables()

#>  [1] "weather"                   "mobility"                 
#>  [3] "epidemiology_england_msoa" "epidemiology"             
#>  [5] "government_response"       "baseline_mortality"       
#>  [7] "diagnostics"               "surveys"                  
#>  [9] "world_bank"                "world_bank_time_series"   
#> [11] "administrative_division"   "spatial_ref_sys"          
#> [13] "geography_columns"         "geometry_columns"
